hese sketches allow one to set a grid of motion detection spots using a camera. Continuous motion over a spot increases the sensor's motion value, which can be useful as a force indicator.

They were first developed for use in the Project FeedNPlay — https://feednplay.dei.uc.pt —, an interactive display in the Department of Informatics Engineering at the University of Coimbra. The project was created by Tiago Martins, João Bicker, and João Cunha, with the support of the First Foundation and DEI.

